Title: Codelocks CL4010 elect tubular mortice with lever
Description: This Codelocks electronic tubular mortice latch outside lever turns freely with no need to operate the latch bolt. The lock's lever will retract the latch bolt when a valid code is entered and the blue LED lights up, the spring lock automatically locking as the door closes for reliable security. A separate key operates management functions and sets the lock into code-free mode. Code-free mode can also be programmed at the keypad using the master code.
